	   <tr><td colspan=2>Re weapons:<br>Without you posting what your weapons are, I can't tell you whether you are, in fact better off with fists or weapon...&nbsp;&nbsp;What you are not addressing at all is the delay associated with fists vs weapons.  A weapon that hits for 10 twice as much as a fist that hits for 15 in a given span of time is clearly better, but going by what your chat window shows will never tell you that.   There is a wealth of information in previous posts here, so take a look at them.  You can check these tables, as wel, and get the definitive answer on the subject. <br><br><a href="http://tinaddar.kung-foo.org/monk1hb.html" target=_new>http://tinaddar.kung-foo.org/monk1hb.html</a> <br><br>Re attack buttons - Each new special attack is better than the previous one, so you can forget about Round Kick.  You'll never need it (or Tiger Claw for that matter once you get past it) again.  So use only one hot key for your special attack.  I use melee, range, special attack, disarm, ID, and bind wound on my combat pad, and I'll swap other abilities into the bind wound position as warranted.<br><br>I have 5 different banks of hot keys - but the most comonly used one contains Sense Heading, Feign Death, Sit, Mend, /loc, and a /assist social.  I have other arrangements for traveling, for pulling, etc etc.<br><br>You won't see a quad hit till level 21, when the probability for a successful DW/DA becomes 2%.  It gets better after that.<br><br>And finally....  For the love of all things holy don't buy a compass!!!  A more counterproductive item I can't think of.  Take the time, get your sense heading up, learn how /loc works, and you'll be forever grateful.<br><br>Keyeluke <br>Monk of the Silent Fist, 44th Circle <br>Strange Brew <br>Druzzil Ro <br><br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a><br>Dripsy - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922</a></td></tr>
